NLSapp.EnableFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF24", False
If Not len(NLSApp.GetField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF2")) = 0 Then 'NLSapp.MessageBox("A Bankruptcy type must be selected before verifying Pacer can be checked." & Chr(13) & "Please try again.") If NLSApp.getField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF24") = "CHECK" and Not NLSApp.getField("TASK_STATUS") = "BK-ACTIVE" then 'NLSapp.SaveScreen() 'NLSapp.SQLSelectStatement("SELECT 0; UPDATE task SET status_code_id = " & TEMPLATE_STATUS_BK_FILED & " WHERE task_refno = " & NLSapp.GetField( "TASK_REFNO")) 'NLSApp.SetSecondaryLoanStatus NLSapp.GetField( "TASK_NLS_REFNO"),NOW(),LOAN_STATUS_BK_FILED,"ADD" 'NLSapp.RefreshScreen()
Else If Not NLSApp.getField("TASK_STATUS") = "BK-NOTICE" then 'NLSapp.SaveScreen() 'NLSapp.SQLSelectStatement("SELECT 0; UPDATE task SET status_code_id = " & TEMPLATE_STATUS_BK_NOTICE & " WHERE task_refno = " & NLSapp.GetField( "TASK_REFNO")) NLSApp.SetSecondaryLoanStatus NLSapp.GetField( "TASK_NLS_REFNO"),NOW(),LOAN_STATUS_BK_FILED,"DELETE" NLSApp.SetSecondaryLoanStatus NLSapp.GetField( "TASK_NLS_REFNO"),NOW(),LOAN_STATUS_BK_NOTICE,"ADD" 'NLSapp.RefreshScreen() End if End if**###After Save###****###After Create###****###After Create###****###On Add Button Clicked###****###On Add Button Clicked###****###Local Functions###** Sub PacerVerification (bktype,filedt,courtval,caseno,pacercheckyn,taskrefno) 'Evaluates 4 fields and if any are not filled it will not enable a field (usredef24) for editing If Not len(bktype) = 0 Then 'A Bankruptcy type must be selected before verifying Pacer can be checked If Not IsDate(filedt) = False Then 'Date filed must be entered before verifying Pacer can be checked If not len(courtval) = 0 Then 'A Court must be selected before verifying Pacer can be checked. If not len(caseno) = 0 Then 'A Case # must be entered before verifying Pacer can be checked. NLSapp.EnableFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF24", True End If End If End If End If
